high_descs: Turn right and walk to a shelf.
Pick up a loaf of bread on the right side of top shelf.
Move to the end table on your right and face its front.
Put the loaf of bread on the end table and make it between the laptop and wall.
Turn left and walk to the shelf next to you; face it.
Pick up the knife in front of the remote control on the shelf.
Turn right and walk to the end table next to you; face it.
Slice the loaf of bread on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Have a loaf of bread on an end table sliced with knife.

high_descs: Turn right towards to the dresser.
Pick up bread from the dresser .
Move towards to the side table.
Place the bread on the side table.
Turn left towards to the dresser.
Pick up knife from the dresser .
Turn right and move towards to the side table.
Sliced the bread on the  side table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up bread, knife from the dresser and sliced the bread on the side table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the dresser
Pick up the bread from the dresser
Move slightly to the right and face towards the side table
Put the bread down on the side table
Move to the left and face towards the dresser
Pick up the knife from the dresser
Move a few feet to the right and face towards the side table
Put the knife on the side table
anns.task_desc: Put the bread and knife on the side table
